Package: BaroWavelet
Type: Package
Title: Baroreflex Sensitivity Assessment with Wavelet Transforms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Alvaro Chao-Ecija <alvarochaoecija.rprojects@gmail.com> [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2691-6936>), 
        Marc Stefan Dawid-Milner [ths]
Maintainer: Alvaro Chao-Ecija <alvarochaoecija.rprojects@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows autonomic evaluation and baroreflex sensitivity assessment
             of interbeat intervals and blood pressure recordings using wavelet transforms. It includes different
             analysis techniques based on the continuous and discrete wavelet transforms. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
